# Generation Pipeline

Follow GENERATION_PIPELINE.md when editing world-generation code.

## Prompt formula (Marble API)

Subject Ôćĺ Materials Ôćĺ Lighting Ôćĺ Spatial. Use commas.

## Pipeline heuristics

- `hasMaterialDetail`, `hasLightingDetail`, `hasSpatialDetail`
- `qualityTier`: weak | ok | strong
- Anti-patterns: hedge words (maybe, kind of, something like)
- `truncateAtWordBoundary`: max 2000 chars

## API

Generate route returns `pipeline_meta`: `{ qualityTier, enhanced, truncated }`. `truncated` comes from processPrompt when input exceeded 2000 chars.
